Gordhan Says Confidence, Investment in South African Economy Is Growing

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-03-08T14:43:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/gordhan-says-confidence-investment-in-south-african-economy-is-growing.html
South African Finance Minister  Pravin Gordhan  said confidence and investment in the economy is
growing.  The government plans to maintain “fiscal sustainability”
and wants to continue its trajectory of higher spending on
infrastructure, Gordhan told lawmakers in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
